budgie-webcam-applet (1.0.3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Added more controllable CIDs
  * Added automatic refresh of device list when video devices are plugged in and out
  * Controls labels now greyed out when disabled
  * Tinkering with UI margins and padding
  * Bugfix: Manual controls are now never disabled when the corresponding automatic control does not exist

 -- Peter Grønbæk Andersen <peter@grnbk.io>  Wed, 19 Nov 2025 12:00:00 +0000


